OL,5,G1230 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe last visit of the week is to
OL,7,     FJohn Graham's The B&B in
OL,8,     FBlackpool, where competition
OL,9,     Fbetween the guests builds during a
OL,10,     Fgame of tenpin bowling. And
OL,11,     Fthere's tension at the dinner
OL,12,     Ftable.
OL,13,G1300 Four in a Bed
OL,14,     FThe B&Bers meet one last time to
OL,15,     Ffind out how much they've been
OL,16,     Fpaid and confront their critics.
OL,17,     FTension runs high, but who will be
OL,18,     Fcrowned best value B&B of the
OL,19,     Fweek?
