OL,5,G1335 Come Dine with Me
OL,6,     FLeeds area. Choir teacher Dionne
OL,7,     Fserves up a menu that mixes
OL,8,     FEuropean and Caribbean flavours,
OL,9,     Fwith a carnival flourish for good
OL,10,     Fmeasure. Does it hit the right
OL,11,     Fnotes for her guests? (Ep1/5)
OL,12,G1405 Come Dine with Me
OL,13,     FLeeds area. Finance director Jane
OL,14,     Fplans a fine dining menu of
OL,15,     Fhomemade ravioli, pork and panna
OL,16,     Fcotta. But Denver is still upset
OL,17,     Fabout Jane calling her a goth.
OL,18,     F(Ep2/5)
