OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt Crackin' View Guest House in
OL,7,     FNorthumberland, Steve and Maria
OL,8,     Freckon their rivals will be blown
OL,9,     Faway by their... cracking view.
OL,10,     FBut there's a bangers clanger at
OL,11,     Fbreakfast.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FAli and his pal Serge host the
OL,14,     Fthird visit of the week, at the
OL,15,     FDomo Boutique Hotel in Birmingham.
OL,16,     FHelen's dazzled by the decor, but
OL,17,     Ftrouble brews over a caffeine
OL,18,     Fconundrum.
