OL,5,G1750 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt The Crown Inn in Norfolk, Lisa
OL,7,     Fand Neil hope that their historic
OL,8,     Fsetting will bag them the B&B
OL,9,     Fcrown. But there are 'paneful'
OL,10,     Fobservations about the windows and
OL,11,     Fa lorry-load of noise.
OL,12,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FOn the final day, the B&Bers
OL,14,     Fdiscover how much they've been
OL,15,     Fpaid. Comments about curtains and
OL,16,     Foff-colour feedback about bedding
OL,17,     Fleave some hosts open-mouthed,
OL,18,     Fbefore the winner is crowned.
